<bibRefCitation author="Wachi, N. &amp; Ide, T. &amp; Abe, Y." box="[1209,1431,639,665]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39" pagination="620 - 626" refId="ref54935" refString="Wachi, N., Ide, T. &amp; Abe, Y. (2011 b) Taxonomic status of two species of Andricus (Hymenoptera: Cynipidae) described by Shinji (1940, 1941) as gall inducers on Cyclobalanopsis. Annals of the Entomological Society of America, 104 (4), 620 - 626. https: // doi. org / 10.1603 / AN 11033" type="journal article" year="2011">
